data.description: Welcome home to East Beach! This beautifully designed home has been carefully maintained. It boasts a 475 sq ft income producing carriage house with hardwood flooring throughout, updated open kitchen, & new hot water heater. The carriage house is one bedroom & one full bathroom. The main house has hardwood flooring throughout & new carpet in the 2 spare bedrooms upstairs. The primary suite has a balcony to enjoy a nice cup of coffee with a book in the mornings. The kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliances, gas stove, and granite countertops. A 2 car garage is connected by a 300 sq ft room with vaulted ceilings, great for entertaining company. The HVAC & furnace have been replaced since new ownership. Dual HVAC system, security system, tankless water heater, Hunter irrigation system, & so much more to offer. The backyard has also been updated with a new gas line. The association amenities are just a stroll away. Make this your home today!
